# Rendered cluster directories — environment-specific but committed for reproducibility.
# These are created by: make new CLUSTER=<name>
# Note: contains Hetzner-specific IPs and node names — not portable across environments.
# GitOps migration (ok-gitops, ADR-Platform-011-candidate): rendered/ will move to
# a dedicated repo/branch; until then, commit rendered manifests here.

# macOS
.DS_Store
__MACOSX/

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Kubeconfigs — never commit
*.yaml.bak
kubeconfig*

# But keep the example and templates
!cluster-config.yaml.example
!templates/
